[[電腦成像|CG]]電影《[[最終幻想VII：降臨之子|最終幻想VII：降臨之子]]》是連接原作結局的2年後<ref>{{cite video| people = Tetsuya Nomura (Director)| date =2008-08-14| title =Final Fantasy VII: Advent Children| medium = DVD| publisher=Square Enix| time =|quote='''Marlene:''' "Sadness was the price to see it end." It's been two years since they told me that. }}</ref>，克勞德和蒂法一起生活在城市外圍，以「快遞」作為職業並讓在新酒吧的蒂法接客戶，放棄了自己原本一個雇傭兵的身分<ref>{{cite video| people = Tetsuya Nomura (Director)| date=2005-09-14| title =Final Fantasy VII: Advent Children| medium = DVD| publisher=Square Enix| time = |quote='''Reno:''' You're our buddy, aren't ya? / '''Rufus:''' Kadaj and his group are young and violent – as dangerous as they come. That's why we decided that it might be in our best to hire a little muscle. / '''Cloud:''' Too bad. I'm a delivery boy now. }}</ref>。和他們住在一起的是巴雷特的養女瑪琳與丹塞爾，是患有致命疾病星痕症候群的孤兒。蒂法幫助丹塞爾、瑪琳一起面對，據透露，克勞德也受到了星痕症候群之苦，在孩子失踪后，面对蒂法，他表示自己並不適合保護他的新家庭和其他朋友們<ref>{{cite video| people = Tetsuya Nomura (Director)| date=2005-09-14| title = Final Fantasy VII: Advent Children| medium = DVD| publisher=Square Enix|quote='''Tifa:''' You have Geostigma, don't you? You're going to give up and die, is that it? So it is. / '''Cloud:''' There's no cure. / '''Tifa:''' Yeah, but, that's not stopping Denzel, is it? Don't run! Let's fight it together! We can help each other, I know we can. I guess ... that only works for real families. / '''Cloud:''' Tifa ... I'm not fit to help anyone – not my family, not my friends. Nobody.}}</ref>。然而，蒂法要他放下過去<ref>{{cite video| people = Tetsuya Nomura (Director)| date=2005-09-14| title =Final Fantasy VII: Advent Children| medium = DVD| publisher=Square Enix| time =|quote='''Tifa:''' Dilly dally, shilly shally! / '''Reno:''' I think she wants you to move on, man. }}</ref>。克勞德到遺忘之城尋找孩子，在那里面对卡達裘、羅茲和亞祖，是萨菲罗斯遺留下来的，還沒來得及完全擴散進到生命之泉中就被遗弃了。<ref>{{cite video| people = Tetsuya Nomura (Director)| date=2005-09-14| title = Final Fantasy VII: Advent Children| medium = DVD| publisher=Square Enix| time =|quote='''Kadaj:''' The stigma. But you know all about that, sir. Mother's memetic legacy lives on in the Lifestream and makes it happen. She does so much for us and we ... we don't even know where to find her. But what can we do? We're just remnants, really remnants of Mother's legacy. Until we find Mother and receive her cells, we can't be whole again! Geostigma and the Legacy aren't enough ... for a true reunion. / '''Rufus:''' What do you mean? / '''Kadaj:''' But, sir! Surely you've noticed ... }}</ref>。在和卡達裘於教堂戰鬥時，由於卡達裘擲出的魔石碰入附近的水池裡，引發一場爆炸，湧出一股和生命之泉結合的清泉，治癒克勞德身上的星痕症候群。成功治癒身體的病痛後，克勞德正式擊敗再度復甦的萨菲罗斯，終結雙方的宿怨，現場留下了垂死狀態的卡達裘<ref>{{cite video| people = Tetsuya Nomura (Director)| date=2005-09-14| title = Final Fantasy VII: Advent Children| medium = DVD| publisher=Square Enix| time =|quote='''Aerith:''' Kadaj? / '''Kadaj:''' Huh? / '''Aerith:''' You don't have to hang on any longer. / '''Kadaj:''' Mother is that ... / '''Aerith:''' Everyone's waiting if you're ready. }}</ref>。克劳德重伤，在生命之泉再度見到札克斯·菲爾和艾莉絲，被生命之泉帶回艾莉絲教堂的地面和夥伴們會合。最終克勞德在教堂群聚的眾人間，望見艾莉絲走向依靠在教堂門口的札克斯的身邊，目送兩者並肩走進強烈的白光裡，才意識到自己始終並非孤身一人，至此解開札克斯和艾莉絲逝世後所留下的心結。

克勞德也出現在中篇小說《[[On_The_Way_To_A_Smile_-_Episode:_Denzel|通往微笑之路]]》中，故事設定於《最终幻想VII》和《降臨之子》間的兩年。「蒂法篇」中他和蒂法一起生活，瑪琳和丹澤爾。「丹塞爾篇」中描述了克勞德如何和丹塞爾第一次見面<ref name="dvd">{{cite video |date=2007-02-20|title = Final Fantasy VII – Advent Children (Limited Edition Collector's Set) |medium = DVD |publisher=Square Enix |location = Japan}}</ref>，后来又被改编成简短的OVA，並包含在《降临之子完整版》中的《通往微笑之路-丹泽尔篇》。克勞德也是[[OVA|OVA]]《[[最終命令_-最終幻想VII-|最終命令 -最終幻想VII-]]》的主角之一，這倒述描述了《最终幻想VII》前的兩事件，離開尼布爾海姆時挺身和萨菲罗斯戰鬥，同時也和札克斯逃避神羅兵的追殺<ref name="lastorder">{{cite video |people= |date=2009-04-10 |title=Last Order: Final Fantasy VII |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0489134/ |medium=DVD |publisher=Square Enix |accessdate=2009-03-10 |time= |quote= |archive-date=2009-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090123115015/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0489134/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

克勞德在《降臨之子》一年後的《[[地獄犬的輓歌：最終幻想VII|地獄犬的輓歌：最終幻想VII]]》中作為一個配角登場<ref>{{cite video game|title=Dirge of Cerberus: Final Fantasy VII|developer=Square Enix|Publisher=SCE America |date=2006-08-15 |platform=PlayStation 2|quote='''WRO Member:''' The WRO was originally established three years ago after Meteorfall. }}</ref>。克勞德、巴雷特和蒂法一起工作，並幫助文森特一起對抗襲擊米德加的神秘DG傭兵<ref>{{cite video game|title=Dirge of Cerberus: Final Fantasy VII|developer=Square Enix|Publisher=SCE America |date=2006-08-15 |platform=PlayStation 2|quote='''Vincent:''' Yeah. And what about you? / '''Cloud:''' What do you think? / '''Tifa:''' Right! You can count on us! / '''Barret:''' When I'm through, there won't be a single sucka standing! / '''Vincent:''' Right. / '''Cloud:''' And as for you... / '''Vincent:''' Don't worry. Leave Deepground to me.}}</ref>。

在《最终幻想VII》的前傳《[[核心危機：最終幻想VII|核心危機：最終幻想VII]]》中，克劳德是一位年轻的神罗士兵，正和札克斯結為好友<ref>{{cite video game|title=Crisis Core: Final Fantasy VII|developer=Square Enix|Publisher=SCE America |date=2008-08-24 |platform=PlayStation Portable|quote='''Zack:''' Good news, Tseng! Me and... / '''Cloud:''' Cloud / '''Zack:''' Me and Cloud here are both backwater experts. Oh yeah!}}</ref>。故事結局時瀕死的札克斯將「毀滅劍」交給了克勞德，並告訴他這是他的遺物，克劳德是札克斯存在的证明<ref>{{cite video game|title=Crisis Core: Final Fantasy VII|developer=Square Enix|Publisher=SCE America |date=2008-08-24 |platform=PlayStation Portable|quote='''Zack:''' Continue living. You are proof that I existed. My dreams and pride, I give it all to you. / '''Cloud:''' I am proof that you existed. }}</ref>。後來克勞德到達了米德加，作為《最终幻想VII》的開端<ref>{{cite video game|title=Crisis Core: Final Fantasy VII|developer=Square Enix|Publisher=SCE America |date=2008-08-24 |platform=PlayStation Portable|quote='''Cloud:''' My name is Cloud. SOLDIER 1st Class.}}</ref>。

克劳德也出现在2020年《最终幻想VII 重制版》中，这也是《[[最终幻想VII补完计划|最终幻想VII补完计划]]》的一部分。 史克威尔称这是对1997年原版游戏的重制，同时声称该游戏还有其他不同的含义。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy VII Remake Is Part Five of the Compilation|url=https://www.siliconera.com/final-fantasy-vii-remake-is-part-five-of-the-final-fantasy-vii-compilation-and-nomura-talks-about-the-term-remake/|accessdate=2020-07-04|date=2020-04-29|work=Siliconera|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200623014955/https://www.siliconera.com/final-fantasy-vii-remake-is-part-five-of-the-final-fantasy-vii-compilation-and-nomura-talks-about-the-term-remake/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 王国之心系列 ===
在《[[王國之心|王國之心]]》，克勞德出現在[[奥林匹斯山|奥林匹斯]][[羅馬鬥獸場|競技場]]的世界。他被描繪為具有爪和深紅色的斗篷，他的劍被包覆在繃帶中。[[野村哲也|野村哲也]]表示，克勞德的左臂是受文森特所啟發，並指出，在這個遊戲中，角色本來是要說明一個「[[惡魔|惡魔]]般」的外觀，因為他關係到「黑暗的一面」<ref name="kh">{{cite book|title=Kingdom Hearts Ultimania: Revised Edition|publisher=Square Enix|location=Japan|language=ja|isbn=4-7575-1349-6|year=2002}}</ref>。他一直被哈迪斯聘請去殺死[[大力士_(1997年電影)|赫拉克勒斯]]，但先決條件是要和[[索拉_(王國之心)|索拉]]交手<ref>{{cite video game|title=Kingdom Hearts|developer=Square|publisher=Square Electronic Arts|date=2002-11-15|platform=PlayStation 2|quote='''Hades:''' That little punk is your next opponent, okay? Now, don’t blow it. Just take him out. / '''Cloud:''' The great god of the Underworld is afraid of a kid? Sorry, but my contract says— / '''Hades:''' I know! You think I don’t know? I wrote the contract! I know it says you’re only required to kill Hercules in this tournament. But you’ve gotta fight that kid to get to him. Come on. Hey, it’s like that old goat says: Rule 11: It's all just a game, so let loose and have fun with it! I mean, a casualty or two along the way is no big deal, right?}}</ref>。戰鬥結束後，哈迪斯放出[[刻耳柏洛斯|刻耳柏洛斯]]攻擊克勞德和索拉，被赫拉克勒斯阻止。後來克勞德向索拉說，他是在尋找一個人<ref name="searching">{{cite video game|title=Kingdom Hearts|developer=Square|publisher=Square Electronic Arts|date=2002-11-15|platform=PlayStation 2|quote='''Cloud''': I'm looking for someone. Hades promised to help. I tried to exploit the power of darkness, but it backfired. I fell into darkness, and couldn't find the light.}}</ref>。後來遊戲透露，在最後的混音，他正在尋找萨菲罗斯。在這遊戲結束後，克勞德和寂靜庭院的居民們團聚。基於內存的版本，使他繼續在系列續作[[Game_Boy_Advance|Game Boy Advance]]的《[[王國之心_記憶之鍊|王國之心 記憶之鍊]]》中作為[[頭目_(角色類型)|BOSS]]出現在奧林匹斯競技場<ref>{{cite video game|title=Kingdom Hearts: Chain of Memories|developer=Jupiter|publisher=Square Enix U.S.A., Disney Interactive|date=2004-12-07|platform=Game Boy Advance|quote='''Cloud:''' I'm not here for the Cup. Just Hercules. Today he loses more than the competition. / '''Sora:''' You don't mean... But why?! What did he do to you? / '''Cloud:''' This is business. Stay out of it.}}</ref>。後成為索拉的召喚卡<ref>{{cite book|last=Hollinger|first=Elizabeth|year=2004|title=Kingdom Hearts: Chain of Memories Official Strategy Guide|publisher=BradyGames Publishing|isbn=0-7440-0473-X}}</ref>。

克勞德再次出現在《[[王國之心II|王國之心II]]》，以他在《降臨之子》的着装出现，並正在尋找萨菲罗斯<ref>{{cite video game|title=Kingdom Hearts II|developer=Square Enix|publisher=Square Enix U.S.A., Buena Vista Games|date=2006-03-28|platform=PlayStation 2|quote='''Sora:''' Oh, Cloud! / '''Donald Duck:''' Whatcha doing? / '''Cloud:''' I'll get him. This time, we settle it. Me, and the one who embodies all the darkness in me. / '''Donald:''' I thought you looked kinda different, Cloud. / '''Cloud:''' If I do, it's his fault. / '''Sora:''' Whose? / '''Cloud:''' Sephiroth. Tell me if you see him. / '''Sora:''' Okay. What's he look like? / '''Cloud:''' Silver hair. Carries a long sword. / '''Sora:''' Sure. Well, be seeing you, Cloud. / '''Cloud:''' Be careful. He messes with your head, makes you think darkness is the only way.}}</ref>，且自己還被蒂法發現<ref>{{cite video game|title=Kingdom Hearts II|developer=Square Enix|publisher=Square Enix U.S.A., Buena Vista Games|date=2006-03-28|platform=PlayStation 2|quote='''Tifa:''' Hey, you! / '''Tifa:''' I'm looking for somebody. Have any of you seen a guy with spiky hair?}}</ref>。[[史克爾·里昂哈特|史克爾·里昂哈特]]的團隊並肩戰鬥襲擊寂靜庭院的[[無心者|無心者]]。應玩家選擇服從萨菲罗斯，贏得了戰鬥，克勞德返回和萨菲罗斯交戰，最后在蒂法给予克劳德支持后，在一個閃光兩人消失而結束。索拉的結論是，克勞德仍和萨菲罗斯戰鬥，直到他被擊敗前都不會停止<ref>{{cite video game|title=Kingdom Hearts II|developer=Square Enix|publisher=Square Enix U.S.A., Buena Vista Games|date=2006-03-28|platform=PlayStation 2|quote='''Goofy:''' Where'd they go? Do ya think they made it back to their own world? / '''Sora:''' They went somewhere else... Cloud went to fight a great battle—to defeat the darkness inside him.}}</ref>。克勞德的複製品亦在《[[王國之心_編碼|王國之心 編碼]]》的奧林匹斯競技場出现，幫助索拉和赫拉克勒斯和哈迪斯交戰<ref>{{cite video game|title=Kingdom Hearts coded|developer=Square Enix|publisher=Square Enix, Disney Interactive Studios|date=2008-11-08|platform=Mobile phone|level=Olympus Coliseum}}</ref>。除了电子游戏外，克劳德还出现在《王国之心》的漫画改编中，重新扮演了他的原始角色。

=== 其他登场 ===

OVA《[[最终命令_-最终幻想VII-|最终命令：最终幻想VII]]》是对尼布尔海姆的毁灭以及札克斯和克劳德从神罗逃脱的重述。由[[MADHOUSE|Madhouse]]制作动画并根据犬中和彦的剧本制作而成，与《最终幻想VII》对事件的描绘不同，例如，通过观察自己的脸来重新解释克劳德对蒂法的营救，尽管《最终命令》与《最终幻想VII》的剧本相关联并对其进行了引用，但它被认为是一部外部作品。克勞德這個角色在《最终幻想VII》外的遊戲也有登場。在《[[神佑擂台|神佑擂台]]》中，克劳德是PlayStation版本中的可玩角色。在[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]]的《[[富豪街系列|富豪街特別版]]》和[[PlayStation_Portable|PlayStation Portable]]的《[[富豪街系列|富豪街：DQ&FF角色大集合攜帶版]]》中，他是可操作的人之一。在《[[陸行鳥大賽車|陸行鳥大賽車]]》中，克勞德作為一個騎著機車的隱藏角色<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.gamespot.com/ps/driving/chocoboracing/hints.html?tag=tabs;cheats | title=Chocobo Racing Hints & Cheats| accessdate=2009-08-15| publisher=GameSpot}}</ref>。在[[PlayStation|PlayStation]]的《[[鬥魂_(遊戲)|鬥魂]]》也有出現，但如其他《最终幻想VII》的角色，他沒有故事情節。於[[最終幻想系列|最終幻想系列]]的[[格鬥遊戲|格鬥遊戲]]《[[最終幻想_紛爭|最終幻想 紛爭]]》中他是代表《最终幻想VII》的角色登場<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.gamespot.com/psp/action/dissidiafinalfantasy/news.html?sid=6195546&mode=previews| author=Niizumi, Hirohiko| title=Dissidia: Final Fantasy Hands-On| accessdate=2010-08-21| date=2008-08-06| publisher=GameSpot| archive-date=2009-04-13| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090413220707/http://www.gamespot.com/psp/action/dissidiafinalfantasy/news.html?sid=6195546&mode=previews| dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的特點是在他《最终幻想VII》衣服，也能使用《降臨之子》的服裝。他和萨菲罗斯的戰鬥是基於《最终幻想VII》和《降臨之子》<ref>{{Cite book | year=2009 | title=Dissidia Final Fantasy Ultimania| url=https://archive.org/details/dissidiafinalfan0000epst | language=ja | publisher=Square-Enix | isbn= 978-4-7575-2488-0 | page=530}}</ref>。隨著整個剧情，克勞德再次登場在前傳《[[最終幻想_紛爭012|最終幻想 紛爭012]]》並作為一個混沌陣營的戰士。他關心蒂法，並試圖獨自打倒卡歐斯，但受了重傷，被女神柯絲摩思救起，並許願在下次戰爭時能成為她的戰士之一。克勞德的主要裝備是基於[[天野喜孝|天野喜孝]]的原始藝術品的概念<ref name="Pre-TGS Flying Get">{{cite web |url=http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2010/09/15/flying_get/ |title=This Week's Pre-TGS Flying Get |publisher=Andriasang |author=Gantayat, Anoop |date=2010-09-14 |accessdate=2010-09-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100916212600/http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2010/09/15/flying_get/ |archivedate=2010-09-16 }}</ref>。他還在[[節奏遊戲|節奏遊戲]]《[[最終幻想_節奏劇場|最終幻想 節奏劇場]]》作為代表《最终幻想VII》一個可玩的角色，穿着《降临之子》中的打扮<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2011/11/12/aerith-snow-vivi-and-faris-are-in-theatrhythm-final-fantasy-too/|title=Aerith, Snow, Vivi, And Faris Are In Theatrhythm: Final Fantasy Too|publisher=Siliconera|author=|date=2011-11-12|accessdate=2012-06-30|archive-date=2013-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131010031057/http://www.siliconera.com/2011/11/12/aerith-snow-vivi-and-faris-are-in-theatrhythm-final-fantasy-too/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在《最终幻想 探险者们》中，完结可以短暂转变为克劳德，以使用他的极限技。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy Explorers Will Let You Transform Into Cloud And Other Final Fantasy Heroes|url=https://www.siliconera.com/final-fantasy-explorers-will-let-transform-cloud-final-fantasy-heroes/|accessdate=2020-07-04|date=2014-08-28|work=Siliconera|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200704044717/https://www.siliconera.com/final-fantasy-explorers-will-let-transform-cloud-final-fantasy-heroes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在《[[小小大星球2|小小大星球2]]》，克勞德是作為一個可下載的人物模型<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2011/07/13/ffvii_lbp2_pack/|title=Final Fantasy VII LittleBigPlanet 2 Costume Pack Hits Tomorrow|publisher=Andriasang|date=2011-07-13|accessdate=2011-07-13|first=Anoop|last=Gantayat|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110714232425/http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2011/07/13/ffvii_lbp2_pack/|archivedate=2011-07-14}}</ref>。

